    • ordinalityColumn

      JpaXmlTableFunction ordinalityColumn(String columnName)
      Defines a long column on the result type with the given name which is set to the ordinality i.e. the 1-based position of the processed element. Ordinality starts again at 1 within nested paths.
      Returns:
      this for method chaining
